:4574,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T11:53:21.000Z","msg":"日韓雙修緊<br />\n讀音韓麻煩好多<br />\n漢字讀音好似"},{"pid":"83cef229bfdf4d185038560493ddb8aaff075fe0","tid":101864,"uid":48473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T13:58:55.000Z","msg":"想問大家背完40音之後下一步會學咩？開始睇書學文法？背字？"},{"pid":"7773faf6fae7714fef0222efe0da4f7895de0dfb","tid":101864,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T14:24:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>日韓雙修緊<br />\n讀音韓麻煩好多<br />\n漢字讀音好似</blockquote><br />\n日語多左/少左個長u音 記日語漢字/詞組讀音<br />\n韓語敬語 外來語拼音 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />記唔到"},{"pid":"382573f350590ab64877ccb72d98b1ce2266d554","tid":101864,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T15:47:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問大家背完40音之後下一步會學咩？開始睇書學文法？背字？</blockquote><br />\n學 自我介紹 ，國家名 家庭成員名，連文法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0f466ae5087cc685b60b704477dbfc98f769392","tid":101864,"uid":75320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T15:51:19.000Z","msg":"Youtube 睇片學 <br />\n有耐心既話一日學到曬basic野"},{"pid":"05e4dc8e17e26764d8528162a877ed5b252726e5","tid":101864,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T16:26:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Youtube 睇片學 <br />\n有耐心既話一日學到曬basic野</blockquote><br />\n有咩 chanel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fd3ea4791bad2f807039b8b41f1f92ba7198ae7","tid":101864,"uid":48473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T05:24:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Youtube 睇片學 <br />\n有耐心既話一日學到曬basic野</blockquote><br />\n有咩 chanel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4