\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢幾日去買書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想問大家會唔會狂背生字？"},{"pid":"4e0c1a2b0f2b62d3428ccac9000f4d509a6af2f8","tid":101864,"uid":54938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T12:27:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Youtube自學發音，之後買本我的第一本韓文文法，d文法都夠基本溝通用，練發音就搵鍾意既慢歌睇韓文字幕，見到識讀既音就大聲讀/唱出黎，會易記好多..</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/FiWw9v6Yibk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FFiWw9v6Yibk&d=DoGI4G7aG2aFCjNgNSWIujPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=3140dc37\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/FiWw9v6Yibk</a><br />\n果時睇呢個學發音</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係睇佢呀！<br />\n岩岩分開三日學完40音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過사同자有啲難分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢幾日去買書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想問大家會唔會狂背生字？</blockquote><br />\n覺得狂背好快冇心機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可能我太廢"},{"pid":"6a56d9a45aba8aa909107d4e7a560b8174addaca","tid":101864,"uid":31650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T12:34:13.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"d2bf81dade78770a646a4462cb6c4268ae6a7206","tid":101864,"uid":30324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T12:37:04.000Z","msg":"自學緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98ba8ae6025c0390331a66a79d8f11cb7ccadcaf","tid":101864,"uid":70042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T12:42:08.000Z","msg":"自學緊<br />\n上網聽晒讀音<br />\n而家睇緊圖解一看就懂的韓語文法書<br />\n比人話呢本書太深 但自己想記晒先<br />\n而家睇到韓文字都識讀 有少少字要慢慢load下"},{"pid":"5c4c0ffb138f0f682cedb39343a950a24e4abde4","tid":101864,"uid":3066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T12:51:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Youtube 睇片學 <br />\n有耐心既話一日學到曬basic野</blockquote><br />\n屌你班人search都賴<br />\n是撚但跟XX老師學