a4","tid":101864,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T14:21:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>八卦一問 大家學完兼背熟所有音用左幾耐時間？</blockquote><br />\n理解到就好易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最麻煩係特殊例子<br />\n同某啲發音喺我地無"},{"pid":"b56cbded9605fb000ca01002f622f3e44c85da1f","tid":101864,"uid":82602,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T14:32:16.000Z","msg":"自學左幾年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係邊睇綜藝邊學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 由識幾個term到宜家可以係韓國大膽咁同人溝通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過好多時都識聽識講唔識寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86c89ffef64dcc2f341e1d884d7868ac536ea688","tid":101864,"uid":40526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T14:32:36.000Z","msg":"自學緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n主要靠睇新聞同報紙專欄查字典<br />\n讀就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff31e1b994dce9c0c59217c167696312f10a4402","tid":101864,"uid":82654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T16:27:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自學左幾年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係邊睇綜藝邊學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 由識幾個term到宜家可以係韓國大膽咁同人溝通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過好多時都識聽識講唔識寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇綜藝真係好有用<br />\n學韓文之前幾年都有keep住睇， 學個陣勁快上手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f312c0aab9d1c61ec5453b5b2fa5bd84b36f0d16","tid":101864,"uid":23632,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T17:27:44.000Z","msg":"ᄏᄏᄏᄏᄏᄏᄏ"},{"pid":"ba9e3cb5b2c416f3cacf6edf9c0b9f9eec5c9117","tid":101864,"uid":48729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T02:13:33.000Z","msg":"我極速學晒啲字母之後，我主要用 talk to me in Korean (TTMIK) 啲資源，加 Anki 生字咭用 Evita sentence deck，另外有用 memrise 加幾本韓文教材：台灣嘅大家的韓國語，延世教材呢啲（千祈唔好用中韓交流，悶到抽筋）。再加 Glossika 嘅 mp3 同埋睇韓國師奶劇。"},{"pid":"f5bbcea44c29fd0ed1ea8b7062d77248c12fb970","tid":101864,"uid":48729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T02:33:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>八卦一問 大家學完兼背熟所有音用左幾耐時間？</blockquote><br />\n一日"},{"pid":"38fca86bca604c519f060d6131d025ba659d6164","tid":101864,"uid":24006,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T02:50:05.000Z","msg":"網上學發音之後買左本《我的第一本韓文書》用完覺得唔夠 就又用延世1-2到宜家<br />\n外加topik1雞精同一本勁厚既文法大全清文法野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n用開naver查字典"},{"pid":"e826141d55d8d76411be7ef140db2728ecc21198","tid":101864,"uid":48729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T02:51:09.000Z","msg":"另外如果本身識日文，可以用韓日詞典<br />\n效果好好多"},{"pid":"3c506ab515e7cb4e8380c60cad96b1b0e4c06af9","tid":101864,"uid":48473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T03:48:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>網上學發音之後買左本《我的第一本韓文書》用完覺得唔夠 就又用延世1-2到宜家<br />\n外加topik1雞精同一本勁厚既文法大全清文法野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n用開naver查字典</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n想問我的第一本韓文書 內容係教文法定係咩？<br />\n我前幾日買左我的第一本韓語文法 不過未開始睇<br />\n想搞清啲發音先 唉好怕會讀錯音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80e85168d923d22e962a929adb797f2107726a16","tid":101864,"uid":29717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T03:54:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>網上學發音之後買左本《我的第一本韓文書》用完覺得唔夠 就又用延世1-2到宜家<br />\n外加topik1雞精同一本勁厚既文法大全清文法野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n用開naver查字典</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n想問我的第一本韓文書 內容係教文法定係咩？<br />\n我前幾日買左我的第一本韓語文法 不過未開始睇<br />\n想搞清啲發音先 唉好怕會讀錯音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"h